There will be a bifurcation of the geopolitical orders which may affect the conditions for growth, but India will do everything it can to ameliorate or mitigate the consequences of a divided world, says Shivshankar Menon, Visiting Professor, Ashoka University and Former National Security Adviser of India at the #SingaporeSummit.


